  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is intended to predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed; all 13 credibility factors were assessed against MRL-5 requirements. Decision: Accepted at low assurance with documented gaps. NOTE: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; structured Context of Use is described in the bound Requirement and Claim prose rather than as a separate hasContextOfUse object.",
